{"title":"回延安","authors":["李季"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":7,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"回延安\t李季\t延安夜月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水数延河清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天数延安蓝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安人儿最相亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安月亮分外圆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山川闪银光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河边歌声喧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着这样的山和水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教人今夜怎安眠？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔上天了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫步延河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望宝塔山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜深云遮月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朦胧看不见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头看延河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延水亲又甜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手掏水饮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔影河心现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心急猛抬头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔光闪闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一望电灯千百盏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再望山川带笑颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长空十万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔天际悬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔形星座入太空！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的宝塔上了天！\t一听说鲁艺来了人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一听说鲁艺来了人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放下锄头往回奔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手紧拉同志的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想你们想坏了这颗心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一听说鲁艺人来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撂下饭碗往外跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边跑着一边叫："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱们的亲人回来了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看你们的大礼堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今成了农具修配厂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个空场你该还记得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们在这里演过《兄妹开荒》。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥儿沟农民和鲁艺的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵蔓菁一条根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托你捎话带个好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥儿沟问候同志们！\t  喜见延安一同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是那双圆口布鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是那身蓝布制服。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窑洞里虽然装上了电灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炕上却还是那床简单的被褥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小米是革命的家常饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荞面餄餎谁不喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了纸烟还不忘旱烟叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“手卷牌”、羊腿巴又香又甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窑洞里还是“连家店”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办公、睡觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又同老乡谈家常。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下乡时还是背着那个小被包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闲了时还爱把小曲儿唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是发白心更红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条皱纹深且长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见面还是像盆红炭火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好同志，这些年你过的怎么样？”\t    1961年7月3日于上海"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}